scopecontent.p:
The collection contains four daguerreotypes executed 1998-2000 by daguerreotypist Jerry Spagnoli. Images include: 
                [Grand Central Station Rededication Ceremony], October 1, 1998, 9 x 22 in. (cased triptych); 
                [Aerial view from 52 West 26th Street with World Trade Center], 1999 (including cased photograph and plate), 4.25 x 3.25 in. (two items); 
                [Macy's Thanksgiving Day Parade], 2000, 6.5 x 8 in. (framed).
